{"tid":1565883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"選舉主任 DQ 前未予機會解釋　劉頴匡選舉呈請勝訴　范國威或失議席","createTime":"2019-09-13T10:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T18:32:58.000Z","uid":120575,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83bf8079620db946d33b55888e1188aa0d9b4292","tid":1565883,"uid":120575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"前年立法會新界東選區補選的劉頴匡，被指支持港獨，遭選舉主任取消參選資格，其後提出選舉呈請。高等法院法官周家明頒下書面判詞，裁定劉頴匡勝訴，當日勝出補選的范國威並非妥為當選。<br />\n<br />\n周家明在判詞中提到，選舉主任在決定取消劉的參選資格，應給予劉頴匡機會解釋，她未有這樣做構成程序不公，因此勝出補選的范國威並非妥為當選。范國威會否失去議席，還要視乎政府會否上訴。<br />\n<br />\n法庭早前亦就香港眾志周庭提出的選舉呈請，裁定案件是違反自然公義及程序不公，周庭沒有被合法地提名，在補選中當選的區諾軒並非適當地當選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/curry-11_oCkKK_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcurry-11_oCkKK_1200x0.png&h=be6d3ac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB-dq-%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%AA%E4%BA%88%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B-%E5%8A%89%E9%A0%B4%E5%8C%A1%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%91%88%E8%AB%8B%E5%8B%9D%E8%A8%B4-%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%E6%88%96%E5%A4%B1%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD/?fbclid=IwAR2vY6D1VlIKnELU-6UgejiBfbnwbSYuUAHERYmgpFfmsfeyyrh3rooMWxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%25BB-dq-%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BA%2588%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2587%258B-%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%25A0%25B4%25E5%258C%25A1%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%2591%2588%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%258B%259D%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E8%258C%2583%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2vY6D1VlIKnELU-6UgejiBfbnwbSYuUAHERYmgpFfmsfeyyrh3rooMWxU&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=3f5e7c63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fth